{"tid":804730,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"差十分鐘開鋪 店員:太早未開門 連兩球生意都唔做","createTime":"2018-09-03T08:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T07:05:03.000Z","uid":4662,"like":147,"dislike":1444,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b60c4f00ca99ac89cdaa8fa8904582708e9b88","tid":804730,"uid":4662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"今朝我同老豆去行街，見到樣好鐘意既野，即刻求我老豆買比我。<br />\n以下係我同老豆既對話<br />\n<br />\n老豆:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老豆：咁早就要？你考慮清楚未？<br />\n我：我想要好耐，求下你買比我。<br />\n老豆：佢望一望價錢牌，話：要兩球咁多！<br />\n我：當係開學禮物，今年唔會再要你買貴野。<br />\n老豆：好啦，一次咁多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我老豆好有型咁行埋去，指住啡色個度示意要買。<br />\n<br />\n點知個店員話仲有十分鐘先開門，唔做我老豆生意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地評下理，差個十分鐘，做生意都唔識靈活變通，祝你快啲執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我頂呀，喊咗好耐，今朝冇雪糕食</span>"},{"pid":"1209fdf930dcbb76aeb2cffed61971b94bd303d3","tid":804730,"uid":106290,"like":387,"dislike":11,"score":376,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"要笑？"},{"pid":"0f318eacf19d1702e35afa291cfc917c5f5a9974","tid":804730,"uid":201309,"like":24,"dislike":62,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"幾幽默"},{"pid":"06592fafb99a285c98f5de91868566c70d8d22bc","tid":804730,"uid":4662,"like":16,"dislike":85,"score":-69,"quote":{"pid":"1209fdf930dcbb76aeb2cffed61971b94bd303d3","tid":804730,"uid":106290,"like":387,"dislike":11,"score":376,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"要笑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"覺得好笑就笑下囉，我不知幾唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106a77268f10540ace6