去，指住啡色個度示意要買。<br />\n<br />\n點知個店員話仲有十分鐘先開門，唔做我老豆生意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地評下理，差個十分鐘，做生意都唔識靈活變通，祝你快啲執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我頂呀，喊咗好耐，今朝冇雪糕食</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>啡色個度</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n樓主想食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？仲要兩球咁多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edf84e5d5b1094875ed519fce5df5bb5d9f50bf","tid":804730,"uid":201266,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/181004_146035e5119eb3894e75538f90617144.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F181004_146035e5119eb3894e75538f90617144.gif&h=884e3e0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e05691937b3d026b9281cc8c49d52a4124c4592","tid":804730,"uid":105614,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:10:16.000Z","msg":"認真 創意ok嘅<br />\n但係我一啲都唔想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeb31c9178044b93c2a8fd94938290e1ac71ae3","tid":804730,"uid":31834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"有時啲嘢唔好隔硬，好肉酸"},{"pid":"38ecd9535118536d992a3b7d5f9e430d295da3c0","tid":804730,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"98c0d54b6bbcd98babdecab2c63fc1b5896ae8e8","tid":804730,"uid":128410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:28:42.00